<div class="slide_question">
<h2>Which is the most common complication of Crohn's disease?</h2>
</div>
<div class="slide_text">
<input id="q11" name="q11" type="hidden" value=""/>
<ul class="radio_inputs">
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="a" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">a</div>
<p>Blockage in the intestine</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="b" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">b</div>
<p>Arthritis</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="c" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">c</div>
<p>Kidney stones</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">13</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>Which is the most common complication of Crohn's disease?</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Sometimes the swelling and scar tissue that come with Crohn’s can thicken the wall of your intestine. Your doctor might call this an intestinal obstruction because the passage is blocked. </p>
<p>Some people get arthritis, eye or mouth inflammation, and kidney stones or gallstones but these happen less often.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
