<div class="slide_question">
<h2>You're more likely to need surgery for Crohn's if you smoke.</h2>
</div>
<div class="slide_text">
<input id="q12" name="q12" type="hidden" value=""/>
<ul class="radio_inputs">
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="a" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">a</div>
<p>True</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="b" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">b</div>
<p>False</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">13</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>You're more likely to need surgery for Crohn's if you smoke.</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Smoking can worsen your Crohn's symptoms. And it can make you more likely to need surgery. Smokers also tend to have more flares, more complications, and need higher doses of steroids and other medications. So quitting can lower your risk of these problems. It may take you a few tries to kick the habit, but it's worth it, so keep at it! You don't have to do it on your own. Ask your doctor about a program to help you make this change.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
